						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in the Kallēs11vara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription commemorates the death of the son of <hi rend="bold">Kētabōva</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Niṭūru</hi> in a fight during an attack on <hi rend="bold">Hebūru.</hi> The date of the record is the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Chitrabhānu Jyēshṭha śu. Ashṭami, Monday.</hi> The <hi rend="italic">Śaka</hi> year is not given. The characters belong to about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
